    message: is_prompt_gen_stale takes Option<&PromptRecord> rather than (map, rel).
    reasoning: Unlike the other query helpers which take `map` and a key, this helper takes a pre-resolved `Option<&PromptRecord>`. Not contradictory, but the asymmetry with siblings is worth surfacing; caller must do the lookup. Existing code matches this signature, so no change was required.
